      <bioghist id="ref8">
         <head>Biographical/Historical Sketch</head>
         <p>Professor of physics at Stanford University, 1947-1970; head of the Physics Department 1948-1966.</p>
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="ref9">
         <head>Description of the Collection</head>
         <p>Professional correspondence, reports and committee papers relating to Professor Schiff's work at Stanford as well as with the National Academy of Science and NASA. Of note are papers relating to his term as head of the Physics Department at Stanford 1948-66 and as a faculty leader. Also includes mimeographed version of his textbook on quantum mechanics, 1947.</p>
      </scopecontent>
